  m_text: "About the Game \u2013 BukSU Insight\n\nBukSU Insight is a simulation game
    designed to help students learn the process of acquiring and validating a student
    ID, as well as locating essential university facilities through exploration of
    the Bukidnon State University campus.\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
