  m_text: Two of the most important requirements for new BukSU students are obtaining
    a University ID and having it validated. These processes are essential for accessing
    campus facilities and services. However, information about these procedures is
    usually provided only through posters or brief announcements, which may not be
    enough for students to fully understand the steps involved.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
